videoSnippet.title: agadmator's MultiversX Christmas Arena - lichess.org
videoSnippet.description:
LINK to tournament https://lichess.org/tournament/m6lRJZat
Hello everyone and welcome to MultiversX Christmas Arena!
May the fastest and most accurate player win.
Flagging is of course encouraged.

1st PRIZE - 250 EGLD (about $15,750)
2nd PRIZE - 100 EGLD (about $6,350)
3rd PRIZE - 50 EGLD (about $3,150)
(no sharing of prizes!)

Winners will be contacted after the tournament via Lichess for prize distribution.

IMPORTANT : Winners will be contacted by agadmator to recieve their prizes. Prizes will be received in EGLD.
MultiversX (Elrond) are sponsoring and distributing the prizes.

As usual, I will be streaming and showcasing your games.
Enjoy :)
